		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Mentors have decided to dedicate their lives (or what remains of their lives) to teaching and guiding others. Mentors who take to adventuring usually choose a disciple or group to guide to success. Some mentors are concerned with passing on their own legend, and some have been in a supporting role their whole lives. Their magical powers can now pass to others and empower them to succeed under the mentor's presence.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Mentor</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>Skill Expertise, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.DmZ04cq5p8kIvZdp]{Guiding Spirit}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.FrImycFJYpolYrj7]{Lend Expertise}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>10</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.EzkHQiJMIadTqy47]{Inspire Breakthrough}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.0DPaOpKp98xuKSjt]{Inspire Greatness}</p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
